    "text": "LONDON, April 25 (Reuters) - Whitbread plc said it would spin off its Costa Coffee business, leaving it with its Premier Inn hotels operation, with the split expected to be completed within 24 months.\nIt said Costa Coffee was the clear UK market leader and second largest globally, and had attractive long-term international opportunities.\nReporting by Paul Sandle; editing by Sarah Young\n ",
